<br>
Earring of the solstice if you can get it.  But some nice HP/MANA items like Velium/Jade rings.  KEI as often as possible since it is probably the most effiecient power-leveling tool available (I once played a druid from 22 to 23 in the 2.5 hour KEI span of time).<br>
